### 1. 计费登录
POST {{ host }}/api/bill/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "kfadmin",
  "password": "kfadmin123"
}

> {%
    // 将响应中的 token 存储到变量 {{token}} 中
    var token = response.body.data.token;
    client.global.set("token",token);
%}


###2. 批量增加 1天卡.
POST {{ host }}/api/bill/card/batch-add
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{ token }}

{
  "cardType": 1,
  "days": 1,
  "num": 35
}

